DOC.HEADLINE: BRIEFCASE : REAL_ESTATE ; HOUSING PERMITS ISSUED IN FIRST_HALF OF 1994 REACH 5-YEAR HIGH
DOC.TEXT: Nearly 8 # 000 housing permits were issued in Orange County during the first_half of the year , the biggest total for that period in five years , according to the Construction_Industry Research Board . Builders took_out 7 # 966 housing permits , compared to 3 # 276 permits for the first_half of 1993 , the Burbank-based real_estate group reported . The last time the total for the six-month period was higher was in 1989 , when 8 # 890 permits were issued .
